A beautiful dish from Thyme restaurant in Athlone
      
Close
 A beautiful dish from Thyme restaurant in Athlone / John and Tara Coffey's Thyme restaurant in Athlone received a well-deserved Michelin Bib Gourmand this year, so it's sure to be on lots of foodie Christmas lists this year. The wild mallard breast with braised leg, organic pumpkin, chard and wild blackberry is sublime. thymerestaurant.ie lucindaosullivan.com Sunday Indo Life Magazine 
